{"tid":265150,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[人中撚] 東京關西廣島16日之尾道仁涯町","createTime":"2017-05-31T12:09:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T12:15:16.000Z","uid":42925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c0f9bf8ba1336bd30a5240007d65a2829af7496e","tid":265150,"uid":42925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T12:09:17.000Z","msg":"5月頭去左東京關西廣島16日<br />\n東京關西應該大家都睇下厭 就唔講了 有人想知先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我行程大概係東京-&gt;飛機-&gt;關西-&gt;新幹線-&gt;廣島-&gt;關西走<br />\n我就主力講廣島啦 比較少人講<br />\n我留左係廣島3日<br />\n第一日去宮島 第二日去兔島 第三日去睇原爆同尾道<br />\n<br />\n首先我就係大阪去新大阪站坐新幹線去廣島 用廣域廣島JR 5日PASS 上網買平$100 -&gt; $8xx (唔想賣廣告) <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/ea8ed6af1871d172465113b4de507982.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fea8ed6af1871d172465113b4de507982.jpg&h=65178c0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/d3c75edd79733ea754a411a877d62b15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fd3c75edd79733ea754a411a877d62b15.jpg&h=3b6be973&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新幹線好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n坐個半鐘就到廣島了<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/572a5f09f7cc33eaf1eb309c2349d5bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F572a5f09f7cc33eaf1eb309c2349d5bf.jpg&h=d515e757&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n轉JR 直接去宮島口轉船去宮島 (JR pass包哂)<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/e5a9421ac70bce6aa961e992b8c3c144.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fe5a9421ac70bce6aa961e992b8c3c144.jpg&h=2d2d5750&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/a5d69a5175b03db3d4d9ef108cf9622e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fa5d69a5175b03db3d4d9ef108cf9622e.jpg&h=5ebb756a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n坐十幾分鐘就到了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你 日本周圍都有鹿既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/95e8aa6fb15e8225ea1cb5554be11c76.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F95e8aa6fb15e8225ea1cb5554be11c76.jpg&h=ffe4db0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n撞到有台妹學校交流團?<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/62224962a7d7af6d52df8e01e3b3ebb1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F62224962a7d7af6d52df8e01e3b3ebb1.jpg&h=6dcfdc66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n宮島名物1-飯勺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/9e8bd973bceb219021079a858afca414.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F9e8bd973bceb219021079a858afca414.jpg&h=a641a052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n宮島名物2-嚴島神社 (其實座島叫宮島定嚴島<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/47941f5f4f86ccaae898cdb9aa986ed7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F47941f5f4f86ccaae898cdb9aa986ed7.jpg&h=59632ed9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好有仁王feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宮島名物3-水中鳥居 (當日潮漲要7點幾 唔等了)<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/ec8e70823e609d2cc08031a28b0a06b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fec8e70823e609d2cc08031a28b0a06b9.jpg&h=29cc974c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本天氣好正 曬但唔熱 行幾個鐘都仲好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食飯先 遲D再講 有乜問題都可以問下我 我答到盡答"},{"pid":"d4ddb2e127f78a19c1bae3d13c74dad2293a2621","tid":265150,"uid":42925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T12:15:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/265158/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/265158/page/1</a><br />\n開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}